| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4755 — Recovery Inhibition (play)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f2bfdf70-54ef-5d5a-aae9-f8cc931d0f1e"
